The park has an artificial lake for boating.

list.abstract: artificial（英[ˌɑːtɪˈfɪʃl]，美[ˌɑːrtɪˈfɪʃl]），英语单词，指模仿天然材料由人工制造的东西，侧重真伪对比。形容词，释义为人工的；人造的；虚伪的。常见短语搭配有artificial intelligence（人工智能）。例句：Artificial intelligence is growing rapidly.（人工智能发展迅速。） artificial的近义词为synthetic、false、simulated；反义词为natural。artificiality为名词，释义为人工；不自然；不自然之物。artificially为副词，释义为人工地；人为地；不自然地。
《ARTIFICIAL》是由Ondrej Angelovic制作发行的一款第一人称物理解谜游戏。

yingyinNormal.en: This artificial beach resort can hold up to 10,000 visitors.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个人工沙滩度假区可容纳一万名游客。

yingyinNormal.en: Right. Different rules for us. Nice guy, artificial. Thank you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧， 评判我们的规则是不同的，人不错。但是个人工智能 。谢谢捧场。

yingyinNormal.en: Howard, artificial women are your department. You want to take this?
yingyinNormal.zh: 霍华德，人造女性是属于你的研究部门的，你要接这个茬吗？

yingyinNormal.en: And I imagine this is the very definition of A.I., artificial intelligence?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我猜想这就是所谓人工智能的定义？

yingyinNormal.en: So you're going for artificial intelligence and you don't want to tell the team?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你要研究人工智能，还不想告诉团队？

yingyinNormal.en: The spin and phoniness and artificial nastiness that saturate so much of our national debate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那些天花乱坠的虚假与龌龊，饱受了太多的国民非议。

yingyinNormal.en: And the odds that a few of them just might give us an advantage over runaway artificial intelligence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有一定的机率其中有一部分人能帮我们对付失控的人工智能。

yingyinNormal.en: As a theory for understanding the human mind, perhaps, but not as a blueprint for building an artificial one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 作为理解人类心智的理论，也许是吧，但作为创造机器人的蓝图，依然是可用的。

yingyinNormal.en: See, I guess another thing I probably should've told you about Ginger is that she kinda has a artificial leg.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我应该告诉你们，金吉儿，她其实装了假支。

yingyinNormal.en: They deep sixed the data but I gotta guess he was knocking on a very particular door. Artificial intelligence.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们清空了数据，但我估计他就要完成一项非常特别的研究了。人工智能。

yingyinNormal.en: The rules have changed. We're dealing with something new. Well the Vision is artificial intelligence. A machine.
yingyinNormal.zh: 规则变了，我们正和新事物在打交道。幻视其实是人工智能 。是一台机器。

yingyinNormal.en: I know an Artificial Intelligence is trying to kill me. I just don't know why. That's what we're trying to figure out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道有台人工智能想杀我，就是不知道为什么。这也是我们想知道的。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay. What artificial satellite has seen glimpses of Einstein's predicted frame dragging? And of course, it's gravity probe B.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好的，哪颗人造卫星记录下了爱因斯坦预言的时空结构拖曳现象？答案是引力探测器B卫星。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't have to do that for me, Gloria. I usually spend Valentine's Day selling artificial flowers near the well in my village.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不用为了我这么做，歌洛莉亚，情人节我通常都在村子里那口井附近卖手工花。

yingyinNormal.en: But world pop is more about breaking and tearing down age-old stereotypes, the artificial confines that have kept us apart for way too long.
yingyinNormal.zh: 世界流行音乐更加地打破老旧的刻板印象，打破那种将我们隔开太久的人工界线。

yingyinNormal.en: And for the many landlocked Chinese, traveling to far-flung seaside resorts is not an option. The answer created the world's largest artificial beach.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而对于许多居住在内陆的中国人来说，去遥远的海滨度假胜地是不现实的。这个问题催生出了世界上最大的人造沙滩。

yingyinNormal.en: It breaks down instantly, disintegrates all the artificial barriers that we've created between each other government, nationality, black, brown, yellow, white, whatever color you are, and shows each other our hearts, our fears, our hopes and our dreams.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它能瞬间瓦解我们之间制造的所有人为的障碍，政府，国籍，黑色，棕色，黄色，白色，不管你是什么人种，它让我们分享内心，分享恐惧，分享希望，分享梦。

artificial修饰事物时指“非自然环境所产生的，人造的”，形容人时则指“言谈举止做作或不自然的”。如：
Her artificial manner made me sick.
她那装腔作势的样子令我恶心。

examination_example.sentence: In a few decades, <highlight>artificial</highlight> intelligence (AI) will surpass many of the abilities that we believe make us special.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 再过几十年，那些我们自认为与众不同，独一无二的能力都将被人工智能 (AI) 所超越。

examination_example.sentence: New electric engines coupled with <highlight>artificial</highlight> intelligence and autonomous systems will contribute to a more efficient, integrated transport system.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 新的电动发动机加上人工智能和自动系统将有助于建立一个更高效、更一体化的运输系统。

examination_example.sentence: A lot of clever people are terrified about <highlight>artificial</highlight> intelligence, fearing that robots will one day become so smart that they'll murder all of us.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 许多聪明人对人工智能感到恐惧，担心有一天机器人会变得非常聪明，以至于他们会杀死我们所有人。

examination_example.sentence: When Elon Musk says that his new priority is using <highlight>artificial</highlight> intelligence to build domestic robots, we should look forward to the day in admiration.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当 Elon Musk 说他的新工作重点是使用人工智能来制造家用机器人时，我们应该怀着钦佩的心情期待这一天的到来。

examination_example.sentence: Professor Godel has a much rosier outlook on the future of <highlight>artificial</highlight> intelligence than, say, Elton Musk, Stephen Hawking, Bill Gates or Steve Wozniak.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)、斯蒂芬·霍金(Stephen Hawking)、比尔·盖茨(Bill Gates)或史蒂夫·沃兹尼亚克(Steve Wozniak)等人相比，戈德尔教授对人工智能的未来前景要乐观得多。

examination_example.sentence: Professor Shook Godel of Georgia Tech developed an sacrificially intelligent teaching assistant to help handle enormous number of student questions in the online class, Knowledge Based <highlight>Artificial</highlight> Intelligence.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 佐治亚理工学院的肖克·戈德尔教授开发了一种人工智能教学助手，来帮助处理“基于人工智能的知识”这门网课中大量的学生提问。

examination_example.sentence: The students, who were studying <highlight>artificial</highlight> intelligence, were interacting with the virtual assistant and couldn't tell it apart om a real human being.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 学习人工智能的学生们与虚拟助手互动，并不知道她不是真人。

examination_example.sentence: Drawing in adventure seekers and experienced divers, this new <highlight>artificial</highlight> Airbus reef will be a scuba diver's paradise (天堂) .
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这个新的人工空客珊瑚礁将吸引探险爱好者和经验丰富的潜泳者，它将成为潜泳者的天堂。

examination_example.sentence: Not only will the sunken plane create the perfect skeleton for <highlight>artificial</highlight> reef growth, but authorities hope this new underwater attraction will bring tourists to the area.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这架沉没的飞机不仅将为人工珊瑚礁的形成搭建完美框架，而且当局还希望这个新的水下景点能为该地区带来游客。

examination_example.sentence: Can <highlight>artificial</highlight> intelligence (AI) machines act ethically, meaning can they be honest and fair?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 人工智能(AI)机器的行为是否符合道德规范，也就意味着它们能否做到诚实和公平吗？
